{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/product-offerings.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>HackerOne is the #1 hacker-powered security platform that helps organizations find and fix critical vulnerabilities before they're criminally exploited.</p>\n<p>HackerOne offers 5 different products that you can choose from:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>HackerOne Response</li>\n<li>HackerOne Bounty</li>\n<li>HackerOne Challenge</li>\n<li>HackerOne Clear</li>\n<li>HackerOne Pentests</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"hackerone-response\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hackerone-response\" aria-label=\"hackerone response permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HackerOne Response</h3>\n<p>Establish an ISO 29147 compliant disclosure policy to safely receive and act on vulnerabilities discovered by external third-parties. This welcomes a \"See Something, Say Something\" process that helps ensure that security reports end up with your security team instead of unreliable channels like social media.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"overview-2\"\n        title=\"overview-2\"\n        src=\"/static/369a2b370bc2b14f9951fdf4028a9f15/0b533/overview-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/369a2b370bc2b14f9951fdf4028a9f15/fac75/overview-2.png 125w,\n/static/369a2b370bc2b14f9951fdf4028a9f15/63868/overview-2.png 250w,\n/static/369a2b370bc2b14f9951fdf4028a9f15/0b533/overview-2.png 500w,\n/static/369a2b370bc2b14f9951fdf4028a9f15/1d69c/overview-2.png 750w,\n/static/369a2b370bc2b14f9951fdf4028a9f15/00d43/overview-2.png 1000w,\n/static/369a2b370bc2b14f9951fdf4028a9f15/56e36/overview-2.png 1750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"hackerone-bounty\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hackerone-bounty\" aria-label=\"hackerone bounty permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HackerOne Bounty</h3>\n<p>A program where trusted hackers are incentivized to continuously test for critical vulnerabilities. Bounty programs can be private and invite-only or fully public, and all incentives will reflect the organizationâ€™s priorities.</p>\n<p>You can choose between 2 types of programs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A managed program enables HackerOne to design, manage, and support your program from end to end.</li>\n<li>A hosted program enables you to run and manage your own program.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"overview-3\"\n        title=\"overview-3\"\n        src=\"/static/327faecaa09d193cb3c337662396ed02/0b533/overview-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/327faecaa09d193cb3c337662396ed02/fac75/overview-3.png 125w,\n/static/327faecaa09d193cb3c337662396ed02/63868/overview-3.png 250w,\n/static/327faecaa09d193cb3c337662396ed02/0b533/overview-3.png 500w,\n/static/327faecaa09d193cb3c337662396ed02/1d69c/overview-3.png 750w,\n/static/327faecaa09d193cb3c337662396ed02/00d43/overview-3.png 1000w,\n/static/327faecaa09d193cb3c337662396ed02/2e694/overview-3.png 1048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"hackerone-challenge\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hackerone-challenge\" aria-label=\"hackerone challenge permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HackerOne Challenge</h3>\n<p>A private, project-based, and time-bound security test. Challenges are perfect for organizations that need focused, time-constrained security testing ahead of major initiatives such as new product releases, code reviews, feature releases, or tightly focused spot checks on key assets.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"overview-1\"\n        title=\"overview-1\"\n        src=\"/static/a12f3f477ced02dcf906c24dfaab11c5/0b533/overview-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a12f3f477ced02dcf906c24dfaab11c5/fac75/overview-1.png 125w,\n/static/a12f3f477ced02dcf906c24dfaab11c5/63868/overview-1.png 250w,\n/static/a12f3f477ced02dcf906c24dfaab11c5/0b533/overview-1.png 500w,\n/static/a12f3f477ced02dcf906c24dfaab11c5/1d69c/overview-1.png 750w,\n/static/a12f3f477ced02dcf906c24dfaab11c5/00d43/overview-1.png 1000w,\n/static/a12f3f477ced02dcf906c24dfaab11c5/0faf1/overview-1.png 1956w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"hackerone-clear\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hackerone-clear\" aria-label=\"hackerone clear permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HackerOne Clear</h3>\n<p>A program that requires proven hackers to be background-checked in order to participate in them. Only hackers that are background-checked are able to participate in such programs due to the sensitive nature of their systems.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"HackerOne Clear overview\"\n        title=\"HackerOne Clear overview\"\n        src=\"/static/de06009b5d2e637cba9cd477e5b2f28f/0b533/overview-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/de06009b5d2e637cba9cd477e5b2f28f/fac75/overview-4.png 125w,\n/static/de06009b5d2e637cba9cd477e5b2f28f/63868/overview-4.png 250w,\n/static/de06009b5d2e637cba9cd477e5b2f28f/0b533/overview-4.png 500w,\n/static/de06009b5d2e637cba9cd477e5b2f28f/1d69c/overview-4.png 750w,\n/static/de06009b5d2e637cba9cd477e5b2f28f/00d43/overview-4.png 1000w,\n/static/de06009b5d2e637cba9cd477e5b2f28f/95c1f/overview-4.png 2330w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"hackerone-pentests\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hackerone-pentests\" aria-label=\"hackerone pentests permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HackerOne Pentests</h3>\n<p>Authorized hackers simulate a cyberattack on a specific application to test how secure the application is. HackerOne pentests are performed by select hackers from the HackerOne community with skills and experience that best match your applications in scope.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"HackerOne Pentests\"\n        title=\"HackerOne Pentests\"\n        src=\"/static/cccde6072a41b6c4a33de49696d1e9d7/0b533/hackerone-pentests.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cccde6072a41b6c4a33de49696d1e9d7/fac75/hackerone-pentests.png 125w,\n/static/cccde6072a41b6c4a33de49696d1e9d7/63868/hackerone-pentests.png 250w,\n/static/cccde6072a41b6c4a33de49696d1e9d7/0b533/hackerone-pentests.png 500w,\n/static/cccde6072a41b6c4a33de49696d1e9d7/1d69c/hackerone-pentests.png 750w,\n/static/cccde6072a41b6c4a33de49696d1e9d7/00d43/hackerone-pentests.png 1000w,\n/static/cccde6072a41b6c4a33de49696d1e9d7/ec09f/hackerone-pentests.png 1916w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"next-steps\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#next-steps\" aria-label=\"next steps permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Next Steps</h3>\n<p>If you've decided to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Start a HackerOne Bounty or Response program, see: <a href=\"program-starting-point.html\">Program Starting Point</a>.</li>\n<li>Start a HackerOne Challenge program, send a note to challenge@hackerone.com.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/product-offerings.html","id":"programs/product-offerings","title":"Product Offerings","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"HackerOne Response"},{"value":"HackerOne Bounty"},{"value":"HackerOne Challenge"},{"value":"HackerOne Clear"},{"value":"HackerOne Pentests"},{"value":"Next Steps"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}